\par 19. y\'fczy\'fdl\'fdn ilk yar\'fds\'fdndan bu yana atomun s\'fdrlar\'fdn\'fd ortaya \'e7\'fdkarabilmek i\'e7in y\'fczlerce bilimadam\'fd y\'fdllarca \'e7al\'fd\'fet\'fd. Atomun \'feekli, hareketi, yap\'fds\'fd ve di\'f0er \'f6zelliklerini g\'fcn\'fd\'fe
