\par _ Takibeden d\'f6nemde, evrenin s\'fdcakl\'fd\'f0\'fd 1 milyar dereceye d\'fc\'fem\'fc\'fet\'fcr. Bu s\'fdcakl\'fdk g\'fcne\'feimizin merkez s\'fdcakl\'fd\'f0\'fdn\'fdn 60 kat\'fdd\'fdr. \'ddlk d\'f6nemden bu d\'f6neme kadar ge\'e7en s\'fc
