\par Cismin rengi, \'fd\'fe\'fdk kayna\'f0\'fdndan gelen \'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fdn \'f6zelli\'f0ine ve s\'f6zkonusu cismin bu \'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fdn ne kadar\'fdn\'fd d\'fd\'fear\'fd yans\'fdtt\'fd\'f0\'fdna ba\'f0l\'fdd\'fdr. \'d6rne\'f0in bir elbisenin rengi, g
